{"tid":2029031,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(長知識) \"攬炒\" 的英文","createTime":"2020-05-22T05:21:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-22T07:12:24.000Z","uid":280539,"like":3,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"5a1df1e58f222cef0fe83cbfa5b6971dd03092b1","tid":2029031,"uid":280539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T05:21:12.000Z","msg":"首先邀請你地睇一條高質討論. RTHK, 當然要睇!<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/L4GoC8S2Xm4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FL4GoC8S2Xm4&d=SoQ3z30fPgPyNEU4M2c%2BSmlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=ac6b912f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/L4GoC8S2Xm4</a><br />\n<br />\n今日同法律同學仔討論打國際綫, 覺得, 尤其係睇完 Ben Sir 條片之後,<br />\n &quot;攬炒&quot; 個味道, 完全翻譯唔到英文.<br />\n咁攬炒作爲我地抗爭中咁重要一個元素, 無個英文, 真係覺得Kick 手 Kick 腳, 有D失色.<br />\n<br />\n小弟斗膽試下推薦 &quot;<span style=\"color: red;\">KAMIKAZE</span>&quot;.<br />\nKamikaze 個字其實係日文, 意思係神風攻擊隊. 個字係我係中學讀歷史既時候第一次接觸到!<br />\n當年 II 戰 艦艇上有對空槍炮, 一般飛機好難飛到上空掉炸彈. 係海戰上一面倒之際, 日本戰機部隊為左當時扭轉該場局勢, 發明左一種新的, 並極度有效的攻擊模式!<br />\n<br />\n戰機機師唔再携帶笨重既炸彈, 子彈, 機槍, 改帶儘量多的燃油用於搜索, 然後一堆戰機發現目標后, 通過高空俯衝既方式直接撞落架艦艇度, 將戰機搖身一變, 變成我地今日既導向飛彈, 戰鬥力加强百倍萬倍! 同時因爲艦艇槍炮都係設計黎針對上空水平橫飛既飛機, 所以對正面飛黎既飛機效果好差. <br />\n<br />\n係一連串既Kamikaze行動當中, 約3,800名 機師因此犧牲, 同時約帶走敵軍 7,000. 當年讀歷史時, 真係讀到喊....<br />\n而久而久之, Kamikaze 今日既意思就既係攬炒.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kamikaze\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FKamikaze&d=SoQ3z30fPgPyNEU4M2c%2BSmlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=ce71a0ba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kamikaze</a>"},{"pid":"ba1f85526ae0e13345f84d9efb890f378d1a4e64","tid":2029031,"uid":102700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T05:23:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df4a1a19139255d6ea382ee900e4e0fe148e699a","tid":2029031,"uid":198503,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T05:25:17.000Z","msg":"Phoenixism = 攬炒"},{"pid":"3b2544d147f5f7329fbac0b7ebe62c3904105254","tid":2029031,"uid":197121,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df4a1a19139255d6ea382ee900e4e0fe148e699a","tid":2029031,"uid":198503,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T05:25:17.000Z","msg":"Phoenixism = 攬炒"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T05:29:28.000Z","msg":"有重新既意味"},{"pid":"407ee674dd934c5c60262d233168a153dd5b76dd","tid":2029031,"uid":29929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T05:30:58.000Z","msg":"If we burn you burn with us"},{"pid":"8eef7a2e50dd0278975c6ff9dbfa8f82cf0af58a","tid":2029031,"uid":138479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T05:31:48.000Z","msg":"fire tgt"},{"pid":"5b5bbf6d92010b19c53f282b51e27f1c04263091","tid":2029031,"uid":56546,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T05:37:31.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n外國撚Kamekazi一向都係咁用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e221f0e6fa38b45351dd5c946d0b2aa7f4af2954","tid":2029031,"uid":143582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T05:39:38.000Z","msg":"<del>kamehameha</del><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fcc08c14a4cd18e022c85b2454ea31692d91031","tid":2029031,"uid":280539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b5bbf6d92010b19c53f282b51e27f1c04263091","tid":2029031,"uid":56546,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T05:37:31.000Z","msg":"係<br />\n外國撚Kamekazi一向都係咁用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T05:39:58.000Z","msg":"YEA!!! 多謝支持!!"},{"pid":"eea129a2af56d6fc5c28c00e96ef313ec917ec43","tid":2029031,"uid"